FUNGAL CONTAMINATION, COCA-COLA PRODUCT - POLAND
**************************************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Fungicide poisoning, Coca Cola - Belgium 990615211523
